<subSubSection id="1FD5651DFFD2FFC2FA34F37A693DED59" pageId="7" pageNumber="312" type="conservation">
<paragraph id="57703696FFD2FFC2FA34F37A693DED59" blockId="7.[1438,2646,2646,3466]" pageId="7" pageNumber="312">
<emphasis id="65BBEA84FFD2FFC2FA34F37A69B2ECFC" box="[1440,1786,3201,3230]" pageId="7" pageNumber="312">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
CITES Appendix II. Classified as Data Deficient on The IUCN Red List. Information on the conservation status of the Golden-white Tassel-ear Marmoset remains scant although it is thought to be threatened by development along the Trans-Amazonian Highway, which has opened up its hitherto inaccessible range to exploitation.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
